{"title":"每日一句","slug":"读书笔记/每日一句","date":"2023-03-31T16:10:23.000Z","updated":"2023-05-09T01:24:31.850Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/读书笔记/每日一句.json","excerpt":null,"covers":["https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/1695961f05f79cb6bf630ce9747a189d.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/0dfd35fcad9190747d8bd3cd2c91c758.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/5d786d9265a8ab5afd6756a5644c52e4.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/cd76763eae593021bc84d2fa51f64a9d.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/6050344edfd2490aeb505e3011edd794.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/97cd8f0106dcfd19988878bcf04bcb7f.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/60c4b0b16daa6141b4dc1b9c9dc1b652.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/7eec7cadfcc61cbebc851e1d4ef748ad.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/b42419f347ac7f02d5c8a8fa27a0b4b0.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/4554d94172a2a7c696338d3744e31bc0.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/596afbbd67fa0de3ea7c72ea08cf4a31.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/6d165fd799704d83bd897da859ee34cb.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/8fcbb628d2d0a7db7526a71e3be1a5fa.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/931eb280f7da7fa5031b58583dcb3d7d.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/c13c845a3f6533ff44bdf1c3bf7c72c3.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/dfd21bd8e8da5f6de3a18a57671ca567.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/2d6c2f0270c4a0d2950a401f57b4840d.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/94b19e65ca9aed680b3d4b278a9796ce.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/0e07c7a1c33d03bb1d0cf334a63d5b02.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/6286d34c787320416bc8d7083e6f6553.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/56c97a833e642283c5252bb049132045.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/d25483d75a1e273417e499f1b63dff94.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/60579abb2ef8eab929cbf832dc1c476f.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/dc1b49d2d9359741bb49f0a936ef6ec7.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/c3fbcf027da73cc5094078f03c60d13c.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/f2f54a47b6952f7c06f21107cbc79386.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/360e1d9aa105dd2b61ad808bcbb06c87.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/f477e4f959ad22efc5d25574f16fdf3c.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/e3e0bf111b67e2be8ccd6d661f4978ba.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/355cae6938c5917aaf90f3116c383367.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/d94da24cd59af49ee0f15d0d6d66a259.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/4c8ea38265f5eaac6f49936fd14d29f6.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/5ef2de07881f42bf9f36f650953ec04a.jpg","https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/d486eb38c2ccb2a54de3d155a66eb31f.jpg"],"content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"/assets/css/APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"/assets/js/APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><script class=\"meting-secondary-script-marker\" src=\"/assets/js/Meting.min.js\"></script><p>【en】You are free to choose your own path.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/1695961f05f79cb6bf630ce9747a189d.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】笑到最后才笑得最好。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】He who laughs last laughs best. </p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/0dfd35fcad9190747d8bd3cd2c91c758.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】积极的思考带来更多的快乐。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Positive thinking initiates more happiness!</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/5d786d9265a8ab5afd6756a5644c52e4.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】擅长的事情，绝不能白干。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】If you are good at something, never do it for free.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/cd76763eae593021bc84d2fa51f64a9d.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】我们来自不同的世界，但我们彼此相容。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】We are from different worlds, yet we fit together.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/6050344edfd2490aeb505e3011edd794.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】你若盛开，蝴蝶自来。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】The better you become, the better you attract.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/97cd8f0106dcfd19988878bcf04bcb7f.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】答应自己要坚强，不让任何事物烦扰内心的平静。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Promise yourself&nbsp;to be so&nbsp;strong&nbsp;that nothing can disturb your peace of mind.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/60c4b0b16daa6141b4dc1b9c9dc1b652.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】生活是一场大冒险。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】To live would be an awfully big adventure.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/7eec7cadfcc61cbebc851e1d4ef748ad.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】你可以随心所欲，但不能随波逐流。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】You can do whatever you want, but you can’t drift with the tide.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/b42419f347ac7f02d5c8a8fa27a0b4b0.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】你定上火车票了吗？</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Have you booked your ticket?</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/4554d94172a2a7c696338d3744e31bc0.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p>**【zh】经历逆境会让你知道谁是真正的朋友。 **</p>\n<p>【en】Adversity does teach you who your real friends are.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/596afbbd67fa0de3ea7c72ea08cf4a31.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】透过失败的迷雾，才能瞥见胜利的光辉。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Failure is the fog through which we glimpse triumph.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/6d165fd799704d83bd897da859ee34cb.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】别杞人忧天了，活在当下。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Take a break from worrying about what you can’t control. Live a little.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/8fcbb628d2d0a7db7526a71e3be1a5fa.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】有时候拒绝会让事情变得更好。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Sometimes things go better when you just say no.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/931eb280f7da7fa5031b58583dcb3d7d.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】凡是成功就要付出代价。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】No victory comes without a price.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/c13c845a3f6533ff44bdf1c3bf7c72c3.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】你的信任是我前进的动力。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Your faith is all that keeps me going.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/dfd21bd8e8da5f6de3a18a57671ca567.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】是好还是坏，只要做你自己就好。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Be good. Be bad. Just be yourself.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/2d6c2f0270c4a0d2950a401f57b4840d.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】不会捕鱼的人，只会把河水弄浑。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Those who can’t fish will only muddy the river.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/94b19e65ca9aed680b3d4b278a9796ce.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】有些人因罪恶而升迁，有些人因美德而没落。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Some rise by sin, and some by virtue fall.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/0e07c7a1c33d03bb1d0cf334a63d5b02.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】诸邪退散！</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Kill the evil out!</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/6286d34c787320416bc8d7083e6f6553.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】我们都在负重前行。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】We all carry something with us.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/56c97a833e642283c5252bb049132045.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】是时候开始过自己想要的生活了！</strong></p>\n<p>【en】It’s time to start living the life you’ve imagined!</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/d25483d75a1e273417e499f1b63dff94.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】做好保暖，凛冬将至。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Brace yourself. Winter is coming.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/60579abb2ef8eab929cbf832dc1c476f.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】医生手册写道：开怀大笑，睡个好觉，此乃灵丹妙药 。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】A good laugh and a long sleep are the best cures in the doctor’s book.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/dc1b49d2d9359741bb49f0a936ef6ec7.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】怕什么？做梦就做的大一点儿！</strong></p>\n<p>【en】You mustn’t be afraid to dream a little bigger!</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/c3fbcf027da73cc5094078f03c60d13c.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】虎年行大运。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Good luck in the Year of the Tiger.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/f2f54a47b6952f7c06f21107cbc79386.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】不费力气，一无所得。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Nothing for nothing.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/360e1d9aa105dd2b61ad808bcbb06c87.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】应该抗议时却保持沉默，这种罪过使人成为懦夫。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】To sin by silence when we should protest makes cowards out of men.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/f477e4f959ad22efc5d25574f16fdf3c.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】爱意东升西落，浪漫至死不渝。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Love rises in the east and falls in the west, romance lasts till death.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/e3e0bf111b67e2be8ccd6d661f4978ba.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】上帝借由各种途径使人变得孤独，好让我们可以走向自己。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】God makes people lonely in a variety of ways so that we can go to ourselves.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/355cae6938c5917aaf90f3116c383367.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】愿人生静好，岁岁含香。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】May life be quiet and sweet every year.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/d94da24cd59af49ee0f15d0d6d66a259.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】当一切都在走下坡时，要向上看。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】When things are looking down, look up.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/4c8ea38265f5eaac6f49936fd14d29f6.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】人的生命是有限的，可是为人民服务是无限的。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Human life is limited, and serving the people is infinite.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/5ef2de07881f42bf9f36f650953ec04a.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">  \n\n<p><strong>【zh】自律是自由的首要条件。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Self-discipline is the first condition of freedom.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/d486eb38c2ccb2a54de3d155a66eb31f.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">     ","more":"<p>【en】You are free to choose your own path.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/1695961f05f79cb6bf630ce9747a189d.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】笑到最后才笑得最好。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】He who laughs last laughs best. </p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/0dfd35fcad9190747d8bd3cd2c91c758.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】积极的思考带来更多的快乐。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Positive thinking initiates more happiness!</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/5d786d9265a8ab5afd6756a5644c52e4.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】擅长的事情，绝不能白干。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】If you are good at something, never do it for free.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/cd76763eae593021bc84d2fa51f64a9d.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】我们来自不同的世界，但我们彼此相容。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】We are from different worlds, yet we fit together.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/6050344edfd2490aeb505e3011edd794.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】你若盛开，蝴蝶自来。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】The better you become, the better you attract.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/97cd8f0106dcfd19988878bcf04bcb7f.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】答应自己要坚强，不让任何事物烦扰内心的平静。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Promise yourself to be so strong that nothing can disturb your peace of mind.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/60c4b0b16daa6141b4dc1b9c9dc1b652.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】生活是一场大冒险。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】To live would be an awfully big adventure.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/7eec7cadfcc61cbebc851e1d4ef748ad.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】你可以随心所欲，但不能随波逐流。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】You can do whatever you want, but you can’t drift with the tide.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/b42419f347ac7f02d5c8a8fa27a0b4b0.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】你定上火车票了吗？</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Have you booked your ticket?</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/4554d94172a2a7c696338d3744e31bc0.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p>**【zh】经历逆境会让你知道谁是真正的朋友。 **</p>\n<p>【en】Adversity does teach you who your real friends are.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/596afbbd67fa0de3ea7c72ea08cf4a31.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】透过失败的迷雾，才能瞥见胜利的光辉。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Failure is the fog through which we glimpse triumph.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/6d165fd799704d83bd897da859ee34cb.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】别杞人忧天了，活在当下。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Take a break from worrying about what you can’t control. Live a little.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/8fcbb628d2d0a7db7526a71e3be1a5fa.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】有时候拒绝会让事情变得更好。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Sometimes things go better when you just say no.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/931eb280f7da7fa5031b58583dcb3d7d.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】凡是成功就要付出代价。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】No victory comes without a price.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/c13c845a3f6533ff44bdf1c3bf7c72c3.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】你的信任是我前进的动力。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Your faith is all that keeps me going.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/dfd21bd8e8da5f6de3a18a57671ca567.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】是好还是坏，只要做你自己就好。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Be good. Be bad. Just be yourself.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/2d6c2f0270c4a0d2950a401f57b4840d.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】不会捕鱼的人，只会把河水弄浑。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Those who can’t fish will only muddy the river.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/94b19e65ca9aed680b3d4b278a9796ce.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】有些人因罪恶而升迁，有些人因美德而没落。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Some rise by sin, and some by virtue fall.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/0e07c7a1c33d03bb1d0cf334a63d5b02.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】诸邪退散！</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Kill the evil out!</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/6286d34c787320416bc8d7083e6f6553.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】我们都在负重前行。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】We all carry something with us.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/56c97a833e642283c5252bb049132045.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】是时候开始过自己想要的生活了！</strong></p>\n<p>【en】It’s time to start living the life you’ve imagined!</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/d25483d75a1e273417e499f1b63dff94.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】做好保暖，凛冬将至。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Brace yourself. Winter is coming.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/60579abb2ef8eab929cbf832dc1c476f.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】医生手册写道：开怀大笑，睡个好觉，此乃灵丹妙药 。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】A good laugh and a long sleep are the best cures in the doctor’s book.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/dc1b49d2d9359741bb49f0a936ef6ec7.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】怕什么？做梦就做的大一点儿！</strong></p>\n<p>【en】You mustn’t be afraid to dream a little bigger!</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/c3fbcf027da73cc5094078f03c60d13c.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】虎年行大运。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Good luck in the Year of the Tiger.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/f2f54a47b6952f7c06f21107cbc79386.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】不费力气，一无所得。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Nothing for nothing.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/360e1d9aa105dd2b61ad808bcbb06c87.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】应该抗议时却保持沉默，这种罪过使人成为懦夫。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】To sin by silence when we should protest makes cowards out of men.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/f477e4f959ad22efc5d25574f16fdf3c.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】爱意东升西落，浪漫至死不渝。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Love rises in the east and falls in the west, romance lasts till death.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/e3e0bf111b67e2be8ccd6d661f4978ba.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】上帝借由各种途径使人变得孤独，好让我们可以走向自己。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】God makes people lonely in a variety of ways so that we can go to ourselves.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/355cae6938c5917aaf90f3116c383367.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】愿人生静好，岁岁含香。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】May life be quiet and sweet every year.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/d94da24cd59af49ee0f15d0d6d66a259.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】当一切都在走下坡时，要向上看。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】When things are looking down, look up.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/4c8ea38265f5eaac6f49936fd14d29f6.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">\n\n<p><strong>【zh】人的生命是有限的，可是为人民服务是无限的。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Human life is limited, and serving the people is infinite.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/5ef2de07881f42bf9f36f650953ec04a.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">  \n\n<p><strong>【zh】自律是自由的首要条件。</strong></p>\n<p>【en】Self-discipline is the first condition of freedom.</p>\n<img src=\"https://staticedu-wps.cache.iciba.com/image/d486eb38c2ccb2a54de3d155a66eb31f.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%\" alt=\"img\">     ","categories":[{"name":"读书笔记","path":"api/categories/读书笔记.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"笔记","path":"api/tags/笔记.json"}]}